 ---------------------------------------------------------------
	Design by contract ( DBC )
	Do no Repeat Yourself ( DRY )

     1. Remove duplicate functionality ( DRY )
     2. Enforce assertions, when assertions are made ( DBC )
     3. Audit memory managment code regularly
     4. Unit testing

